    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long neck chains worn loosely from the shoulders and usually extending below the waist.  May have a pendant or tassel suspended at the bottom.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
